description:
The Pirate looked rusty in her last match with Bobbie Starr, she dominated but not in the manner we are use to. Is she 100% back from her season 2 ending injury?
The Assassin is back for her second match, she is tough flexible, and determined. However today was her day to get totally dominated in all three rounds. She got fingered fucked, during the wrestling, and fucked hard like a loser in RD4. Not the outcome she was hoping for. Real, unscripted wrestling at its best.
title: The Pirate(12-1)
